These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Sport: swimming, handball, cycling
1. Sport:handball is on the right of Sport:cycling##1
2. Sport:swimming is on the far right##1
3. Sport:swimming is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Sport   | cycling | handball | swimming |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
Food: nectarine, kale, broccoli
1. Food:kale is in an odd position##4
2. Food:nectarine is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Food   | nectarine | broccoli | kale |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Hobby: fishing, puzzles, card-games
1. Hobby:puzzles is in an even position##4
2. Hobby:puzzles is on the left or right of Hobby:card-games##3
3. Hobby:card-games is on the right of Hobby:puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Hobby   | fishing | puzzles | card-games |

 #################################
 
